Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.72,0:01:43.92,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur8}満身創痍のこの身を　捧げよう
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.92,0:01:46.84,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur8}Take one step and you gotta move on
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.84,0:01:49.54,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur8}Don’t retreat never looking back on
